---
import PolicyBlock from '../PolicyBlock.astro';
import PolicySection from '../PolicySection.astro';
---

<PolicyBlock
  id="privacy-habitos"
  title="Habits AI"
  badgeLabel="Privacy Policy"
  updated="July 17, 2026"
>
  <PolicySection heading="Overview">
    <p>
      Ball Studios ("we", "our") operates the mobile application
      <strong>Habits AI</strong> (package ID:
      <code>com.ballstudio.habitos.app</code>).
      This document describes how data is collected and used when you use the App.
      Habits AI is a habit tracker and personal productivity tool that also offers an
      AI coaching feature and an optional cloud backup via Firebase.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Data we collect">
    <p>
      Habits AI is built local-first: your habits, goals, diary entries, mood logs,
      audio voice memos, and points are stored on your device and never transmitted
      to our servers unless you choose to sign in. When you use the optional
      Google sign-in, the following additional data may be collected:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google account display name and email address (used only for account identification)</li>
      <li>A Firebase user ID linked to your account</li>
      <li>Habit and goal data synced to Firestore for backup and cross-device access</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      You can use the App fully without creating an account. Anonymous usage does
      not transmit any personal data to our servers.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="AI coach">
    <p>
      The App includes an <strong>AI coaching feature</strong> powered by DeepSeek. In compliance
      with the <strong>EU AI Act</strong> (in force August 2026), we inform you that this feature
      uses an artificial intelligence system to generate personalized habit advice.
      <strong>You are always interacting with an AI, not a human coach.</strong>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      When you use the AI coach, a summary of your habit and goal activity is sent to a secure
      backend proxy (hosted on Render) which forwards the request to
      <strong>DeepSeek</strong> (operated by DeepSeek AI, People's Republic of China).
      This summary contains aggregated habit statistics only — it does not include your name,
      email, diary entries, voice memos, or any directly identifying information.
      Requests are not stored by Ball Studios beyond the session duration.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      <strong>International transfer notice:</strong> DeepSeek is based in China, a country
      without an EU adequacy decision. By using the AI coach, you acknowledge that your
      anonymized habit statistics will be transferred to and processed in China under
      DeepSeek's terms. If you do not wish this transfer, do not use the AI coach feature —
      all core habit-tracking functionality remains available without it.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      DeepSeek's data practices are governed by
      <a href="https://www.deepseek.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek's Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Advertising">
    <p>
      The App uses <strong>Google AdMob</strong> to display rewarded ads. Watching
      a rewarded ad is optional and unlocks additional AI coach interactions.
      AdMob may collect data to serve personalized ads, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Device identifiers (Advertising ID)</li>
      <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
      <li>Interaction data with displayed ads</li>
      <li>App usage information</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      You can opt out of personalized advertising in your device settings under
      <em>Privacy → Ads</em>. Google's data practices are governed by
      <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="In-app purchases">
    <p>
      The App offers an optional premium subscription processed by
      <strong>Google Play</strong>. We do not receive or store payment card details.
      All transactions are governed by
      <a href="https://play.google.com/about/play-terms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play's Terms of Service</a>.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Push notifications">
    <p>
      With your permission, the App sends local push notifications as habit reminders
      and weekly review prompts. These notifications are scheduled on your device and
      do not involve transmitting personal data to our servers. You can disable
      notifications at any time in your device settings.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Children's privacy">
    <p>
      The App is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
      personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided personal
      information, contact us and we will delete it promptly.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Data deletion">
    <p>
      Local data can be removed at any time by uninstalling the App. If you signed
      in with a Google account, you can request deletion of your Firebase data by
      contacting us at the address below and we will process the request within
      30 days. You can also export and delete your data using the backup and restore
      feature inside the App's profile screen.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Lawful basis (EEA & UK)">
    <p>Where we process personal data, the lawful basis under GDPR is:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contract</strong> — account data (name, email, Firebase ID) required to provide cloud sync and the signed-in service</li>
      <li><strong>Consent</strong> — personalized advertising via AdMob (EEA/UK); AI coach data transfer to DeepSeek</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — non-personalized ads; anonymous usage analytics to improve the App</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      Anonymous (non-signed-in) usage involves no personal data processing by Ball Studios.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Your rights">
    <p>If you are in the EEA, UK, or California, you have the following rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
      <li><strong>Portability</strong> — receive your habit and goal data in a structured format (available via the App's export feature)</li>
      <li><strong>Objection</strong> — object to processing based on legitimate interest</li>
      <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> — withdraw AI coach or ad consent at any time without affecting other features</li>
      <li><strong>Opt-out of data sharing</strong> (California) — opt out of ad data sharing via device settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      To exercise these rights, contact us at
      <a
        class="about-cta"
        href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMVe3zWAij_TeCoYU03qG2ggQVVJMWYmuq8J1hfybdmcohpg/viewform"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="Open Ball Studios questionnaire"
      >
        Contact
      </a>
      We will respond within 30 days.
    </p>
  </PolicySection>

  <PolicySection heading="Contact">
    <p>
      Questions about this policy:
      <a
        class="about-cta"
        href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMVe3zWAij_TeCoYU03qG2ggQVVJMWYmuq8J1hfybdmcohpg/viewform"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="Open Ball Studios questionnaire"
      >
        Contact
      </a>
    </p>
  </PolicySection>
</PolicyBlock>
